---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Work With Us | Media Kit — Filce.uk" description="Partner with filce.uk for authentic product reviews. We create in-depth, photography-rich reviews for tech, home automation, tools, and smart home products." canonicalPath="/media-kit/">
  <div class="page-container">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>Work With Us</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Partner with filce.uk for authentic product reviews</p>
      </header>

      <div class="page-content prose">
        <p class="lead">Thanks for your interest in partnering with filce.uk. We create honest, in-depth reviews with real product photography and hands-on testing.</p>

        <h2>About filce.uk</h2>
        <p><strong>filce.uk</strong> is a UK-based review site focused on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>🏠 <strong>Home Automation</strong> — Home Assistant, smart devices, sensors</li>
          <li>🔧 <strong>Tools</strong> — DIY, workshop, and hobbyist equipment</li>
          <li>📱 <strong>Tech Accessories</strong> — Practical tech for everyday use</li>
          <li>🐕 <strong>Pet Tech</strong> — Products for pet owners (we have a Malamute!)</li>
          <li>🍳 <strong>Kitchen & Home</strong> — Gadgets that make life easier</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Audience</h2>
        <p>We target UK consumers who:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Research before buying</li>
          <li>Value authentic, hands-on reviews</li>
          <li>Want practical, jargon-free content</li>
          <li>Appreciate real product photos</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        
        <h3>Product Reviews</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Hands-on testing</strong> — We actually use the product</li>
          <li><strong>Real photography</strong> — Your product shown in use, not stock images</li>
          <li><strong>Detailed write-ups</strong> — 1,500-3,000 words covering features, use cases, pros/cons</li>
          <li><strong>SEO-optimised</strong> — Structured for search visibility</li>
          <li><strong>Amazon affiliate links</strong> — Direct path to purchase</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Content Types</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Full product reviews</li>
          <li>Comparison articles</li>
          <li>Buying guides</li>
          <li>Category roundups</li>
          <li>Setup tutorials</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What We're Looking For</h2>
        <p>We're particularly interested in:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Ubiquiti</strong> — UniFi networking, cameras, access points</li>
          <li><strong>Reolink</strong> — IP cameras, NVR systems</li>
          <li><strong>Smart home brands</strong> — Home Assistant compatible devices</li>
          <li><strong>DIY/Tool brands</strong> — Quality tools for hobbyists</li>
          <li><strong>Pet tech</strong> — GPS trackers, smart feeders, cameras</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Process</h2>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Contact</strong> — Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@filce.uk">contact@filce.uk</a></li>
          <li><strong>Discussion</strong> — We'll discuss your product and timeline</li>
          <li><strong>Review</strong> — Hands-on testing (2-4 weeks typical)</li>
          <li><strong>Draft</strong> — We'll share the review for factual accuracy</li>
          <li><strong>Publish</strong> — Live on filce.uk with affiliate links</li>
          <li><strong>Promotion</strong> — Social sharing as agreed</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Review Policy</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>We <strong>do not</strong> accept payment for positive reviews</li>
          <li>We <strong>do</strong> accept review units (kept or returned as agreed)</li>
          <li>We <strong>always</strong> disclose if a product was provided</li>
          <li>We <strong>will</strong> mention flaws honestly</li>
          <li>We <strong>won't</strong> review products we can't genuinely recommend</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@filce.uk">contact@filce.uk</a><br>
        <strong>Response Time:</strong> 48-72 hours</p>

        <hr>

        <p><em>We're a new site actively building our review portfolio. If you're a brand looking for honest, detailed coverage, we'd love to hear from you.</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
